Adriane Lenox https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adriane_Lenox 0 Adriane Lenox (born September 11, 1956) is an American actress, best known for her performances in Broadway theatre. Her performance in the play Doubt: A Parable garnered her the Tony Award for Best Featured Actress in a Play in 2005. She received another Tony Award nomination for After Midnight in 2014.
